title: about
text:
Running Code
When you click the Render button a document will be generated that includes both content and the output of embedded code. You can embed code like this:

1 + 1

[1] 2


You can add options to executable code like this


[1] 4


The echo: false option disables the printing of code (only output is displayed).

title: Alice Giampino
text:
About me
I am a Postodctoral Researcher of Statistical Science at the department of Economics, Management and Statistics (DEMS) of University of Milano-Bicocca.
Research interests: Bayesian clustering; Bayesian nonparametrics; random partition models; applied Bayesian models; computational statistics; topic models.
E-mail: alice.giampino@unimib.it
